The '''most popular given names''' vary [[country|nationally]], [[region]]ally, and [[culture|culturally]]. Lists of widely used [[given name]]s can consist of those most often bestowed upon [[infant]]s born within the last year, thus reflecting the current [[onomastics|naming trends]], or else be composed of the [[personal name]]s occurring most within the total [[population]].
